{"tid":1695362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底成場運動有冇進步過","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:51:53.000Z","uid":193220,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"197bff117d0a580082f63874774c840069a40cee","tid":1695362,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"由六月份到依家<br />\n<br />\n人數不斷送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底有咩方法可以對政府 /777/ 黑警會有致命一擊<br />\n<br />\n罷工又唔撚肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(雖然有人依家組織罷工但係真心希望大家可以一齊罷工)<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔罷工私人公司一樣當你Condom<br />\n照樣莫須有炒你魷魚就好似國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就好想見識黑警見人罷工上門拉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人到底幾時先會進步？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係潑冷水。。。呢個係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況依家美國國會人權法好大機會今年通過唔到<br />\n( 燒山加持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n香港真係靠自己，但係有冇更好方法可以減少送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成場運動由六月份到而家到底有冇進步過...🌚？"},{"pid":"4c6f1a3bb940fadba62ae8026c512dcb4bab67d8","tid":1695362,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:55:52.000Z","msg":"升級已經封頂, 冇得再進步<br />\n掟炸彈或刺殺政要呢d更高等級既手段唯有靠班勇敢的中國人"},{"pid":"804833c688a5b3d3b030c9c6513ee54eeaa34f59","tid":1695362,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5138d46069120dd944e26907dbcda7c2b111f88d","tid":1695362,"uid":127575,"li